questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;Refer to the following letter and symbol series and answer the question that follows. Counting is to be done from left to right only.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
(Left) L R&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;Omega;&lt;/span&gt; Y A $ K ^ T J # Q &amp;amp; # E %&amp;nbsp;S U * &amp;pound; B (Right)&lt;br /&gt;
How many such symbols are there, each of which is immediately preceded by a vowel and also immediately followed by a letter?&lt;/p&gt;<br>&lt;p&gt;निम्नलिखित अक्षर और प्रतीक श्रृंखला का संदर्भ लें और उसके बाद आने वाले प्रश्न का उत्तर दें। गिनती केवल बायें से दायें की जानी है।&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
(बायें) L R &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;Omega;&lt;/span&gt; Y A $ K ^ T J # Q &amp;amp; # E % S U * &amp;pound; B (दायें)&lt;br /&gt;
ऐसे कितने प्रतीक हैं, जिनमें से प्रत्येक के ठीक पहले एक स्वर है और ठीक बाद में एक अक्षर भी है?&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;Given series:&amp;nbsp;(Left) L R&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;Omega;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Y A $ K ^ T J # Q &amp;amp; # E %&amp;nbsp;S U * &amp;pound; B (Right)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Required condition: Vowel &amp;larr; Symbols &amp;rarr;Letter&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Left) L R&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;Omega;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Y &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A $ K&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; ^ T J # Q &amp;amp; # &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;E %&amp;nbsp;S&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; U * &amp;pound; B (Right)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Two symbols are there, each of which is immediately preceded by a vowel and also immediately followed by a letter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal;  line-height: normal; &quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &amp;ldquo;&lt;b&gt;Option 1&lt;/b&gt;&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;दी गई शृंखला: (बायें) L R &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;Omega;&lt;/span&gt; Y A $ K ^ T J # Q &amp;amp; # E % S U * &amp;pound; B (दायें)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;आवश्यक शर्त: स्वर &amp;larr; प्रतीक &amp;rarr; अक्षर&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

